---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Umar Farouk Yunusa" description="Learn more about Umar Farouk Yunusa: backend lead, open source creator, AI engineer, and founder of Real Dev.">
	<section class="space-y-8 py-4">
		<div>
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl mb-6">
				About Me
			</h1>
		</div>

		<!-- Biography Section -->
		<div class="prose">
			<blockquote class="my-6">
				I got into programming by building things before I fully understood what I was building. Over 7+ years I've shipped fintech systems handling 500K+ daily transactions, built AI-integrated platforms before it was fashionable, and spent nights launching open-source tools just to scratch my own itch. I write mostly about backend systems, AI engineering, and the craft of building software that lasts.
			</blockquote>

			<p>
				My technical background centers around backend design, systems architecture, and AI integration. I focus on writing clean, robust, and highly scalable software. Over my career, I have collaborated with international teams across Canada, South Korea, and Nigeria, helping scale platforms from initial ideas into products handling heavy production traffic.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				Beyond regular work, I love creating developer tools. Whether it is a PHP SDK for AI applications, chrome extensions, or attribute-based CSS libraries, I am passionate about simplifying code for other developers.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Facts Section -->
		<div class="pt-6 border-t border-border-custom">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Quick Facts</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span><strong>7+ years</strong> of professional engineering experience across Nigeria, South Korea (MUST Company), and Canada (Manaknight Digital).</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Former <strong>Backend Lead at MUST Company</strong> — a South Korean fintech firm.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Built production <strong>AI systems</strong> integrating Claude, OpenAI, and Gemini with RAG pipelines and multi-agent workflows.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Founder of <a href="https://realdevhq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-custom hover:underline font-semibold">Real Dev</a> — a developer knowledge platform and live talk show.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Currently building <strong class="text-fg-custom">LLMesh</strong>, an open-source PHP AI SDK: <em>"The PHP AI SDK — works everywhere, including Laravel."</em></span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Creator of <strong class="text-fg-custom">Aura CSS</strong> (<code>useaura</code> on npm) — a lightweight semantic attribute-based CSS library with over 1,000+ weekly downloads.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Enrolled in an <strong>MBA</strong> at Bayero University Kano's Dangote Business School.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Shipped projects include: OSBTS, OmniFile, Wazobia Agent, Slack Status Overlay, and more.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
